
Progress bar demo by WebSocket
===================================

download and setup nodejs & git:
https://nodejs.org/
http://git-scm.com/download/

open git:
> cd {tmp directory}
> git clone --recursive https://github.com/npm/npm.git
> cd npm
> node cli.js install npm -gf
> npm config set registry http://registry.npm.taobao.org/

> set NODE_ENV=development

init demo app:
> cd websocket-progress-demo
> npm install

start server:
> npm start
